<view class="order-valuation-container">
  <view class="custom box">
    <view class="orderNum">订单号：20220509140712345678</view>
    <view class="title">
      <view class="shield-icon">
        <image src="../../../assets/images/shield.png"></image>
      </view><text>保价</text>
    </view>
    <view class="input">
      <input type="number" maxlength="10" bindinput="handleCalculate" model:value="{{value}}" placeholder="自定义物品价格，请填写真实物品价格" />
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="valuation1 box">
    <view class="tip">
      <view>
        <van-icon name="warning-o" />
      </view>
      <text class="redtext">国际快递由于多国调度，存在一定比例丢失的情况！如丢失包裹，购买丢失险可获得全额赔付赔付(最高5000元)!</text>
    </view>
    <view class="loss-risk">
      <text>丢失险（保价的3%）</text>
      <van-switch size="40rpx" active-color="#00de64" checked="{{ checked1 }}" bind:change="onChange1" />
    </view>
    <view class="premium">
      <text>保险费：{{premium1}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="valuation2 box">
    <view class="tip">
      <view>
        <van-icon name="warning-o" />
      </view>
      <text class="redtext">电子产品等容易被税的高客单价产品建议购买关税保险!英国关税起征点为0.01英镑!
      综合关税=货值x增值税+(货值+运费+货值x产品税率)x20%+清关杂费。
      </text>
    </view>
    <view class="loss-risk">
      <text>丢失险（保价的2%）</text>
      <van-switch size="40rpx" active-color="#00de64" checked="{{ checked2 }}" bind:change="onChange2" />
    </view>
    <view class="premium">
      <text>保险费：{{premium2}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
<view class="bts">
  <button open-type="contact" class="contact">联系客服</button>
  <button class="next-step" bindtap="handelNextStep">下一步</button>
</view>